      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0651P0-01864'>
        <a name='S5LV0651P0_20030708_GCR_36'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-william-goodhart' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0651P0_20030708_GCR_36' title='Link to this speech by Mr William Goodhart' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
